	<a name="83693024">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<h2>Well, Not So Fast, Sparky</h2><br />Now I don't know exactly how the archive process chooses to update the current archive file.  It didn't do it the way I thought it would when I published the previous note.  It did not catch up to "Well, Yes It Is!"<br /><br />So I don't know the system.  But I am out of my bathrobe and leaving the house!  Places to be, people to see.<br /><br />Ciao, Ciao, ecc.<br>
