	<h2>Archiving Is On?</h2><br />Well, who knows.  I have turned on archiving, requesting once-per-week archives.<br /><br />I also bit the bullet and allowed this page to be made public.   Why not.    We have no secrets here.<br /><br />There is also not a lot to interest people.   <br /><br />Now I have this desire to say something deep and meaningful.  Oh well, it really is time to get out of my bathrobe and look at my calendar and figure out what results I will produce in the rest of the day that I have available.  That is quite enough.<br /><br />Ciao<br>
