	<h3>Reflection on progress so far</h3><br /><b>So leave already.</b>  OK, this is my first session with blogger after signing up this morning.  Most of the notes are technical ones based on my initial experience.  I am going to stop now and collect my thoughts, see how to make better use of this.<br>
